	<h1 class="title">从过气到脱销，就因为乔治小王子穿了Crocs</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75588/small/75588.jpg?1431919455" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张金晶 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-16 16:45:27 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/10879/medium/10879.jpg?1436644917" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


